reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Non Stellar Results
reviews.reviewText: Although item is inexpensive, I had hoped it’s simplicity would be what made it work. I was disappointed because I didn’t get a nice crisp line when shaping a wing, neither with a powder eyeshadow nor with a pencil liner. Liquid liner gave me better results using this gadget, but not foolproof. I will have to go back to using tape, which always works great for me

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I have tried forever to get the perfect wing. I’m 51 and have hooded eyes. I have bought specific brushes, used tape, watched tons of tutorials but always ended up with a terrible wing. That’s until I used this!!!! This made it so simple. I used a very stiff, angled brush and eyeshadow and my wings are beautiful. I have not attempted with liquid liner because that’s too harsh for me at my age. If you need help with a wing, buy this, you won’t regret it!!!
I purchased this to get my eyeliner nice and straight and it works well to create that wing!
